<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10146254>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Microscopic structures of Cyathus tongxinianus (drawn from the holotype, CLZhao 27588). A: Outer wall of peridium. B: Inner wall of peridium. C: Structure of the hairs. Bars: A–C = 10 µm. Drawings by: Zi-Yan Duan." ;
