    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Microscopic structures of Cyathus tongxinianus (drawn from the holotype, CLZhao 27588).A: Basidiospores. B: Generative hyphae of the funicular cord. C: Internal structure of the peridiole. Bars:A–C = 10 µm. Drawings by: Zi-Yan Duan." ;
